{"tid":1970291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共用限聚令打壓黃店！手足我地要反擊！","createTime":"2020-04-13T05:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T08:46:27.000Z","uid":307711,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0ae30512c3fbbaac3725ca86e2e78aab3593d0","tid":1970291,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"1）<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一人一投訴</strong></span></strong>：見到藍店違反限聚令，即刻報狗、報食環、報衛生署(安全情況下影相做證據)<br />\n<br />\n2）<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一share</span></strong>分享資訊到街坊tg group，希望其他附近手足去視察核實，接力投訴<br />\n<br />\n3）<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一開post</span></strong>除咗tg分享，更加可以整合多個違規藍店資料，開post share出去<br />\n<br />\n先post為敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民華餐廳<br />\n東涌富東街6號富東廣場地下21號舖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L8XiJu3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL8XiJu3.jpg&h=4a882d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n復活節幾日假期每張台距離無1.5米(求其搵塊板隔住)/over一半顧客(應該好多係經東涌出發的忽然行山友)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce474a94ba85a5238292efc4a1e1aa98c64e598","tid":1970291,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76eaaa31a53d34735d752543951e3274e58ce114","tid":1970291,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:14:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00cc1a9c1dbced4a8b17fd6a04f8bed33836fb63","tid":1970291,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1403cd0c1ac09c60e134594dd7b74e3396bb5ef2","tid":1970291,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12380abe85bb72be81e8dc505121921b5a615ff0","tid":1970291,"uid":325